headline: Does Incyte’s 2025 Beat And 2026 Guidance Shift The Bull Case For INCY?
summary: Incyte Corporation recently reported past fourth-quarter 2025 results showing revenue of US$1,506.84 million and net income of US$299.28 million, alongside full-year 2025 revenue of US$5.14 billion and net income of US$1,286.65 million, and issued 2026 total net product revenue guidance of US$4.77 billion to US$4.94 billion.
